Further information
Rishworth Aviation on behalf of our client Garuda Indonesia are now accepting applications from CRJ-1000 First Officers for the placement of CRJ-1000 First Officers on a 2 years renewable contract with Garuda Indonesia based in Denpasar, Makassar, Medan, Balikpapan or Jakarta.
Contract Term: 2 years, renewable
Location/Base:  Denpasar, Makassar, Medan, Balikpapan or Jakarta (subject to the airline's final approval).
Ref #: 672
Aircraft Type: CRJ1000
Garuda CRJ-1000 First Officers - Upcoming Screening Dates in 2014  To be Announced Soon – Apply Now
Minimum Requirements
1000+ Jet hours;
500+ FO hours on type;
Valid ICAO licence with current CRJ 200/700/900 or 1000 rating;
Valid Class 1 Medical Certificate;
Valid SIM proficiency check on the CRJ 700/900 or 1000 within the last 6 months;
3 take offs and landings on the CRJ 200/700/900 or 1000 aircraft in the last 90 days; and
ICAO level 4 English proficiency
Benefits
18 consecutive days off every three consecutive months on duty, housing allowance will be provided, per diem allowance when on layover, access to ID90 travel privileges on Garuda's network and medical insurance is provided as part of your contract.
What Next?
When you are close to, or meet the minimum requirements of any job, by registering or logging in, you will have access to further details and can contact us to find out more.
We welcome your application and encourage you to apply for other jobs we have advertised that may be of interest to you.
